Collection of small and simple home-brew scripts

list of scripts with short description:
  hbserver.php       - server for hbclient; should be served by HTTP server
  hbclient.sh        - client for hbserver; should be run from shell
  ripcd.sh           - shell script to rip contents of the Audio CD
  downsample_flac.sh - downsample flac file to 16 bits 44.1kHz sample rate
